Johnny Indrisano https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Johnny_Indrisano 0 Johnny Indrisano (November 1, 1906 — July 6, 1968) was an American welterweight boxer whose career spanned the period from 1923 to 1934. He later became a film stunt performer and bit-part film and TV actor.
